property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'CreatePurchaseRequisitionLine' || '::' || "PurchaseRequisitionLine"."ID"        AS "ID",
    "PurchaseRequisitionLine"."ID"                                                   AS "PurchaseRequisitionLine",
    "PurchaseRequisitionLine"."CreationTime"                                         AS "Time",
    "PurchaseRequisitionLine"."CreatedBy_ID"                                         AS "ExecutedBy",
    "PurchaseRequisitionLine"."CreationExecutionType"                                AS "ExecutionType"
FROM "o_custom_PurchaseRequisitionLine" AS "PurchaseRequisitionLine"
WHERE "PurchaseRequisitionLine"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL

sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT DISTINCT 
    "Event"."ID"  AS "ID",
    "Object"."ID" AS "PurchaseDocumentLine"
FROM "e_custom_CreatePurchaseRequisitionLine" AS "Event"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_PurchaseRequisitionLine" AS "PurchaseRequisitionLine"
        ON "Event"."PurchaseRequisitionLine_ID" = "PurchaseRequisitionLine"."ID"
    LEFT JOIN "r_o_custom_PurchaseRequisitionLine__PurchaseDocumentLines" AS "r_PurchaseDocumentLine"
        ON "PurchaseRequisitionLine"."ID" = "r_PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine" AS "Object"
        ON "r_PurchaseDocumentLine"."PurchaseDocumentLines_ID" = "Object"."ID"
WHERE "Object"."ID" IS NOT NULL
